Title: Bank Application
       This is a banking application developed in IntelliJ IDEA. It provides essential banking functionalities like account management and transactions.
Features:
      Create and manage user accounts
      Deposit and withdraw money
      Check account balance
      View transaction history
Technologies Used:
     Java
     IntelliJ IDEA
     MySQL
Installation:
     Clone the repository: git clone https://github.com/matampallivanitha/Bank_Application.git
     Open the project in IntelliJ IDEA.
     Ensure Java is installed on your system.
     Run the application.
How to Use:
     Launch the application.
     Register a new account or log in.
     Perform banking operations like deposits, withdrawals, and balance inquiries
